{"data":[{"date":"14:50 21/06","title":"M\u1eb9 Messi: \"Con trai t\u00f4i kh\u00f3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG Argentina\"","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/21/me-messi-con-trai-toi-khoc-nhieu-lan-trong-mau-ao-dtqg-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e0 Celia Cuccittini chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n m\u00e0 con trai Lionel Messi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Messi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn khi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn Argentina h\u00f2a Iceland h\u00f4m 16/6. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u1ed1t tr\u1ea7m m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 M10 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n, sau ba l\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec t\u1ea1i World Cup 2014, Copa America 2015 v\u00e0 2016.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u1eb9 Messi Con trai t\u00f4i kh\u00f3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u1eb9 Messi Con trai t\u00f4i kh\u00f3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/mes2-2879-1529552716.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi r\u01a1i l\u1ec7 sau khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u khi\u1ebfn Argentina thua trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Copa America 2016.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb9 Messi chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh El Trece h\u00f4m 20/6: ''M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Messi l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ham mu\u1ed1n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. Gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y n\u00f3 \u0111au kh\u1ed5 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n. H\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai, n\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup n\u0103m nay''.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng, Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Argentina. N\u0103m 2016, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n sau khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Copa America.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n''Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111au kh\u1ed5 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u00e0nh cho Messi. Khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta n\u00f3i Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m khi ch\u01a1i cho Argentina, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eb9. Gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t y\u00eau n\u00f3 v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac'', b\u00e0 Celia cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMessi t\u1eebng tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n s\u1ee9c \u00e9p khi l\u1eadp hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Ecuador trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup (3-1). \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Argentina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0 xem gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu h\u00f2a ho\u1eb7c thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n''T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y Messi \u0111\u00e3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u01b0\u1edbc n\u00f3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn. T\u00f4i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi n\u00f3 h\u00e3y t\u1ef1 vui v\u1ebb, s\u1ed1ng cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. C\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh lu\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 n\u00f3'', b\u00e0 Celia chia s\u1ebb.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3748","checkdouble":"189155"},{"date":"15:15 21/06","title":"VPF l\u1ea1i thu\u00ea tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i V-League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/11/22/vpf-lai-thue-trong-tai-ngoai-lam-viec-tai-vleague.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u VPF \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n Anh T\u00fa \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd m\u1eddi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VPF thu\u00ea tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i V-League  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"VPF thu\u00ea tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i V-League  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/22/vpf-lai-thue-trong-tai-ngoai-lam-viec-tai-vleague.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>VPF thu\u00ea tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ngo\u1ea1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League n\u0103m nay, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 song c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i V-League v\u1eabn l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n b\u1ecb treo c\u00f2i v\u00f4 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VPF \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eddi c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n Anh T\u00fa, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch VPF kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t gi\u1eefa m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 trong ba ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb 18/06 \u0111\u1ebfn 20/06.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, do v\u1eady, Ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u00fang k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n m\u1eddi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i FIFA ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i khi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t \u0111ua tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u0103ng cao s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e2n c\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \"nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m\", Ban \u0110i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh VPF c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi VFF v\u00e0 C\u1ee5c C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t h\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 (B\u1ed9 C\u00f4ng an) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba, b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 trong s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 minh b\u1ea1ch cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3747","checkdouble":"189156"},{"date":"15:31 21/06","title":"Inter Milan h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n sao Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/13/inter-milan-hoi-muon-sao-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Davide Zappacosta c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ef1u sao Torino 1 n\u0103m k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Davide Zappacosta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Davide Zappacosta t\u1eeb Torino, song m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 12 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Davide Zappacosta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Davide Zappacosta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/13/inter-milan-hoi-muon-sao-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zappacosta ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Davide Zappacosta l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, song anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u sao Torino ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Davide Zappacosta song kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter Milan h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Zappacosta</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Davide Zappacosta c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ef1u sao Torino 1 n\u0103m k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zappacosta cua Chelsea\" title=\"Zappacosta cua Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/9/13/Hau-ve-Davide-Zappacosta-noi-ve-su-khac-nghiet-o-EPL-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Inter h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Zappacosta</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh Milan kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t Zappacosta ngay \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t n\u0103m. N\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, Inter s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Inter Milan. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Zappacosta c\u0169ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu Conte \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Stamford Bridge, Zappacosta s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3746","checkdouble":"189154"},{"date":"15:47 21/06","title":"S\u1ed1c: Roy Keane t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n... \"v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u\" tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Ferguson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/soc-roy-keane-tung-muon-vat-dau-tro-ly-hlv-ferguson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u2013 Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRoy Keane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Roy Keane t\u1eebng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. Sau khi r\u1eddi M.U, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169, b\u1edfi anh t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sir Alex &ndash; HLV Carlos Queiroz c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7. \u00d4ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Ferguson v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2002/03, gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i quay l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2004. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Queiroz \u0111ang l\u00e0 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Iran chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 Keane \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c &ldquo;\u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9&rdquo; n\u0103m x\u01b0a.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc&rdquo; &ndash; Keane cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Man United. Carlos Queiroz c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u1edfi m\u1edf cho l\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi nghe s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz khi c\u00f2n \u1edf M.U\" title=\"Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/soc-roy-keane-tung-muon-vat-dau-tro-ly-hlv-ferguson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz khi c\u00f2n \u1edf M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean khi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ra \u0111i, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2004, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Queiroz th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tranh c\u00e3i n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y nghi ng\u1edd l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u l\u1ea1i qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u00f4ng \u1ea5y r\u1eddi b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111e d\u1ecda v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. Carlos Queiroz l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong vai tr\u00f2 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV Ferguson, nh\u01b0ng Carlos Queiroz kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Patrice Evra t\u1eebng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 g\u1ea7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi b\u1ecb Roy Keane mu\u1ed1n v\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea7u Queiroz, HLV n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2008, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n b\u1ecb tr\u00ed HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. \u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2011, \u00f4ng nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Iran cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189082.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/5/26/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-khung-tuyen-duc-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189082.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao kh\u1ee7ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea-172-189132.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o t\u1edbi CLB Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh Ruben Loftus-Cheek m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o CLB Chelsea v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3745","checkdouble":"189159"},{"date":"16:21 21/06","title":"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i MU v\u00e0 Tottenham v\u1ee5 sao Aston Villa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/liverpool-muon-danh-bai-mu-va-tottenham-vu-sao-aston-villa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Jack Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Liverpool-muon-mua-Jack-Grealish-cua-Aston-Villa-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 ghi 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap Aston Villa l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng, song \u0111\u1ec3 thua Fulham.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. MU quan t\u00e2m Jack Grealish, Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Pochettino c\u1ee7a Tottenham c\u0169ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Jack Grealish \u1edf Spurs.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, HLV Klopp \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/liverpool-muon-danh-bai-mu-va-tottenham-vu-sao-aston-villa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Tottenham v\u00e0 MU trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Liverpool ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp r\u1ea5t m\u00e1t tay v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Jack Grealish ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf s\u00e2n Anfield.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAston Villa \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 v\u00f4 danh nh\u01b0 Jack Grealish.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang b\u1ecb dao \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 Aston Villa \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish, 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Aston Villa nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3744","checkdouble":"189164"},{"date":"16:54 21/06","title":"Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n sao kh\u1ee7ng cho Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/arsenal-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-juventus-voi-gia-45-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin c\u1ee7a Arsenal, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus h\u1ecfi mua Bellerin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hector Bellerin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Arsenal. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/arsenal-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-juventus-voi-gia-45-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Bellerin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Theo The Sun, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Bellerin, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Arsenal nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Juventus c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia s\u1ebd c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ngay \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Bellerin</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/juventus-mua-hau-ve-hector-bellerin-176-172922.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Bellerin </span>c\u1ee7a Arsenal, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bellerin\" title=\"Bellerin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/4/Hector-Bellerin-phat-bieu-ve-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Bellerin v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, HLV Unai Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bellerin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i\u00a0sao 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Alexandre Lacazette, Granit Xhaka, Pierre Emerick Aubameyang, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Hector Bellerin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, song Arsenal s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3743","checkdouble":"189169"},{"date":"17:18 21/06","title":"\"MU c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2016/9/22/mk-dons-tha-thiet-moi-chao-ryan-giggs.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, M.U tr\u1eafng tay khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Ryan-Giggs-phat-bieu-ve-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u00e2n binh, bao g\u1ed3m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dalot. 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Giggs khuy\u00ean MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"cuu tien ve Ryan Giggs\" title=\"cuu tien ve Ryan Giggs\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/22/Giggs-muon-tien-ve-Aaron-Ramsey-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ryan Giggs mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Mourinho n\u00ean mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 Rio Ferdinand trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t bi\u1ebft ch\u1ec9 huy h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, M.U s\u1ebd h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM.U c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. Carrick \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, M.U thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ryan-giggs-khuyen-mourinho-ky-hop-dong-voi-sao-real-madrid-172-189040.html\" target=\"_blank\">Giggs c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n MU mua Gareth Bale</span> c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGiggs c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o Mourinho, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n gi\u1ecfi. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c M.U s\u1ebd c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3742","checkdouble":"189170"},{"date":"09:51 21/06","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/u19-viet-nam-tiep-tuc-co-chien-thang-dam-tai-trung-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>G\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn n\u1eefa v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm.</h2><h2>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi CLB Meizhou Meixian Techand v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i B c\u1ee7a CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/DT-U19-Viet-Nam-co-chien-thang-dam-tai-Trung-Quoc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n gi\u00f2n gi\u00e3 khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Meizhou v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-0. V\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o x\u1ea3y ra khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Chung cu\u1ed9c, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp Meizhou 5-0. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 24/6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i B c\u1ee7a CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 26/6. \u0110\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 14/7 t\u1ea1i Jakarta (Indonesia). \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia, Th\u00e1i Lan, Singapore, L\u00e0o, Philippines. B\u1ea3ng B c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Malaysia, Myanmar, \u0110\u00f4ng Timor, Campuchia v\u00e0 Brunei.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Th\u00e1i Lan, Indonesia v\u00e0 Malaysia chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, c\u0169ng s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/DT-U19-Viet-Nam-co-chien-thang-dam-tai-Trung-Quoc-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\">VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Jarkata, Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, U19 \u00dac. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/dtqg/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten-292-188565.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/dtqg/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten-292-188565.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 25 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 v\u00e0 U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/indonesia-goi-hang-khung-tu-chau-au-ve-dau-u19-viet-nam-168-186505.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/17/indonesia-goi-hang-khung-tu-chau-au-ve-dau-u19-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/indonesia-goi-hang-khung-tu-chau-au-ve-dau-u19-viet-nam-168-186505.html\">Indonesia g\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng kh\u1ee7ng t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110T U19 Indonesia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Ba Lan, &ldquo;s\u00e1t th\u1ee7&rdquo; Egy Maulana \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3741","checkdouble":"189137"},{"date":"10:09 21/06","title":"Thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HAGL s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/21/thua-3-tran-lien-tiep-hagl-sap-trinh-lang-ngoai-binh-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c 3 ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 5 t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB HAGL th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi cho l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CLB HAGL th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi cho l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/35744087_2190201994547920_3279057563122925568_n.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB HAGL th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi cho l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kim Jin-seo v\u00e0 Rimario th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, BL\u0110 HAGL \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay th\u1ebf ngo\u1ea1i\u00a0 binh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 HAGL. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar Moreira. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1987 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o HAGL \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i V-League 2016. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh t\u1eebng ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ghi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian Osmar g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi HAGL kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Brazil b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Osmar ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho SLNA tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Osmar, HAGL c\u00f2n th\u1eed vi\u1ec7c c\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng\u00a0Vincent Bossou sinh n\u0103m 1986. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i V-League. Anh c\u0169ng t\u1eebng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Togo tham d\u1ef1 hai VCK CAN 2013 v\u00e0 2017. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n,\u00a0Vincent Bossou \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Highlight-Da-Nang-vs-HAGL-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-hagl-noi-gi-sau-khi-tang-tien-lai-ngua-quen-duong-cu-168-189067.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/6/clb-hagl-noi-gi-sau-khi-tang-tien-lai-ngua-quen-duong-cu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-hagl-noi-gi-sau-khi-tang-tien-lai-ngua-quen-duong-cu-168-189067.html\">CLB HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn l\u1ea1i ng\u1ef1a quen \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169?</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh xung quanh vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn d\u00ednh \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t l\u1ea7n hai v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong-168-188827.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong-168-188827.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 HAGL, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m th\u01b0 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i sau chu\u1ed7i 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u1ea1i V-League...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3740","checkdouble":"189139"},{"date":"09:35 21/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Bale c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/1/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-bale-canh-bao-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jonathan Barnett kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng Bale s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.</h2><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Real v\u00e0o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i m\u01a1 h\u1ed3 sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Liverpool. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Zidane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chia tay Real Madrid. V\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf l\u00e0 Julen Lopetegui.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Bale c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Bale c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-bale-canh-bao-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Bale c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jonathan Barnett kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Lopetegui c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i trao m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho Bale. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-moi-chao-cac-doi-bong-anh-mua-gareth-bale-172-182611.html\" target=\"_blank\">ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Santiago Bernabeu</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 xem m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ti\u1ebfn ra sao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Bale mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean t\u1ed1i th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Bale l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Bale \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Bale, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Bale mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barnett t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bale \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool t\u1ea1i Kiev. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u0103ng quang danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Barnett cho r\u1eb1ng Bale kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec b\u1edfi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Bale h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i hay nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Bale kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng minh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i hay th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Bale r\u1ea5t th\u00edch cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ee9a nh\u00f3c v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd xem. B\u1edfi v\u00ec Bale c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u00e2y gi\u1edd&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-ra-gia-pjanic-it-nhat-80-trieu-euro-176-189062.html\">Juventus b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho Real v\u00e0 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-dai-gia-chau-au-dai-chien-vi-asensio-180-189042.html\">3 \u0111\u1ea1i gia ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec Asensio</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3739","checkdouble":"189133"},{"date":"09:13 21/06","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o t\u1edbi CLB Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/21/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh Ruben Loftus-Cheek m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o CLB Chelsea v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">Loftus-Cheek ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o Chelsea</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">\u00a0</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\" grande\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loftus-Cheek ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o Chelsea  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Loftus-Cheek ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o Chelsea  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/loftuscheek-ra-loi-canh-cao-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Loftus-Cheek mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Chelsea</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 12/2014, cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ruben Loftus-Cheek v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i t\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 31 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o The Blues, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 19 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y sang CLB Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Loftus-Cheek \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u Chelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 c\u00e1c HLV \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e3y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i xem nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u00f9 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u. Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho Chelsea th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u00e0 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung cho World Cup\u201d, Loftus-Cheek n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Loftus-Cheek \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Panama v\u00e0o h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu Dele Alli kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp \u0111\u00f9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3738","checkdouble":"189132"},{"date":"19:07 20/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 20/6: Nh\u1edd thuy\u1ebft kh\u00e1ch MU s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 100 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-206-nho-thuyet-khach-mu-sap-co-bom-tan-100-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 20/6.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1edd thuy\u1ebft kh\u00e1ch MU s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 100 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 206 MU s\u1eafp c\u00f3 bom t\u1ea5n 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 206 MU s\u1eafp c\u00f3 bom t\u1ea5n 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/matic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n Matic thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Milinkovic-Savic t\u1edbi Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM.U \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng Nemanja Matic s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T Serbia tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\"Tim Cahill c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110an M\u1ea1ch\"</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Stan Lazaridis ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Tim Cahill, c\u1ef1u sao \u0110T \u00dac tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 38 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng C.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec Asensio</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo El Gol Digital, MU, Chelsea v\u00e0 PSG l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marco Asensio c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sao tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf Dele Alli</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Loftus-Cheek s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf Alli. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate tin t\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 24/6 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus \u0111\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pjanic khang dinh chi trich Juventus la khong cong bang\" title=\"Pjanic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Juventus l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/Man-City-muon-mua-Miralem-Pjanic-nhung-khong-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Pjanic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Tuttosport kh\u1eb3ngd \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus \u0111\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic, hi\u1ec7n Real, Barca v\u00e0 Chelsea l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria, Massimo Ferrero \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Lucas Torreira s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Mertens\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp thay th\u1ebf Conte mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Dries Mertens \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, The Blues c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wilshere th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Arsenal sau 17 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3737","checkdouble":"189083"},{"date":"02:53 21/06","title":"Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Luis Suarez, c\u1ef1u sao MU ti\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 l\u1eddi m\u1eddi gia nh\u1eadp Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/chuc-mung-luis-suarez-cuu-sao-mu-tien-the-he-lo-loi-moi-gia-nhap-barca.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean Guillermo Varela cho bi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e0n anh tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 tranh th\u1ee7 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o anh v\u1ec1 c\u00f9ng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng x\u00e9t tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ai C\u1eadp, Luis Suarez ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-463-189080.html\" target=\"_blank\">Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia</span> \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u01b0ng v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u sao MU m\u1eebng Luis Suarez ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u sao MU m\u1eebng Luis Suarez ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Thong-ke-Uruguay-vs-Saudi-Arabia---Bang-A-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luis Suarez ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f2n g\u00ec \u00fd ngh\u0129a h\u01a1n khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 100 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Guillermo Varela n\u1ee9c n\u1edf ng\u1ee3i ca sau cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i 25 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Manchester United:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cLuis th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ea3 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barcelona hay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 100 v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn \u1edf World Cup, kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cLuis c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n n\u1eeda \u0111\u00f9a n\u1eeda th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB. Anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 Barca v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1ea3i qua 4 n\u0103m kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Old Trafford, Varela tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Penarol \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, anh c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed chi\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh World Cup 2018 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Varela m\u01a1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barcelona, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0103n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb\u2026 Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-cua-uruguay-truoc-saudi-arabia-421-189108.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-cua-uruguay-truoc-saudi-arabia.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-cua-uruguay-truoc-saudi-arabia-421-189108.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia</span><br>\r\nUruguay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3736","checkdouble":"189114"}]}